Package com.bytedesk.ai.springai.config

Class ChatModelPrimaryConfig

java.lang.Object
com.bytedesk.ai.springai.config.ChatModelPrimaryConfig
@Configuration public class ChatModelPrimaryConfig extends Object
根据spring.ai.model.chat配置动态设置Primary的ChatModel 支持的值：zhipuai, ollama, dashscope, deepseek, baidu, tencent, volcengine, openai, openrouter, siliconflow, gitee, none
